PREHEAT oven to 350 degrees F. COMBINE spinach, artichoke hearts, mayonnaise, sour cream and salt in large bowl; stir well. ADD seasoned cheese; stir to blend. Spoon mixture into medium baking dish; bake uncovered for 30 minutes, or until cheese is melted. SPRINKLE with tomatoes. Serve with tortilla chips, salsa and sour cream.